.claude/*.log

# Claude memory or workspace files you do not want committed
CLAUDE.local.md
CLAUDE.private.md
.claude-memory
.claude-memory.*

# Claude artifacts / generated output folders
claude-artifacts/
claude-output/
claude-generated/

# Visual companion brainstorming sessions
.superpowers/